This directory contains all that's needed to build an F# version of the
F* application library (alib) in order to build F# applications.

Run `make fsharp-lib` from the top level to extract the library,
build it, and run the F# tests.

The `tests/` subdirectory contains small F* programs that are extracted
to F#, compiled, and run.

The output of the library build goes into the bin/ and obj/ subdirectories.
